lead_paragraph: Jean Segura had four hits, including a go-ahead three-run home run in the sixth inning, to lead the Arizona Diamondbacks to a 12-7 win over the St. Louis Cardinals on Monday night.

headline.print_headline: Segura Powers Diamondbacks to Win Over Cardinals
